\par
\par The border\lang1033\f1 -\lang1042\f0 lines are made by Xs again.
\par
\par \cf1\b White\cf0\b0  has \cf1\b 5 points\cf0\b0 , \cf1\b Black\cf0\b0  has \cf1\b 9 points\cf0\b0  inside the Xs.
\par }
