Dia. 03 White's Right
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}{\f1\fswiss\fcharset0 Tahoma;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White has the right to play\lang1033\f1  the\lang1042\f0  hane and connection with 1 and 3, because it is sente.
\par
\par After playing some endgame moves, the one who can play the next move in sente has the \cf1\b right to play it\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par It is very important\lang1033\f1  when\lang1042\f0  counting in the endgame.
\par }
